properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 14 at 2:02PM CST until January 16 at 6:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
waves 6 to 9 feet possible.

* WHERE...Portions of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From Wednesday evening through late Wednesday night.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and waves.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM WEDNESDAY EVENING THROUGH LATE WEDNESDAY NIGHT
